{
  "texts": [
    "Preparation of Benchmark Datasets: For each selected benchmark, datasets were prepared to represent a wide range of contexts and complexities.",
    "These datasets were carefully curated to challenge the models' understanding and explanatory capabilities. 2.",
    "Model Fine-Tuning and Setup: Prior to evaluation, each LLM was fine-tuned using a portion of the benchmark datasets.",
    "This step ensured that the models were optimally prepared for the tasks, with settings adjusted to balance performance and interpretability.",
    "Generation of Model Outputs:The models were then tasked with generating outputs based on prompts or questions derived from the remaining portions of the benchmark datasets."
  ]
}